Junction:      ✅ Working (P:/.claude/skills/reflect → skill/)
SKILL.md:      ✅ Accessible
Hook Script:   ✅ Exists (hook-stop.bat for Windows)
Hook Config:   ❌ NOT configured in settings.local.json
```

**Issue:** The documentation says "always-on" but the hook isn't actually registered in `~/.claude/settings.local.json`. 

**Required:** To make it work as documented, the hook needs to be added:

```json
{
  "hooks": {
    "Stop": [{
      "matcher": "*",
      "hooks": [{
        "type": "command",
        "command": "P:\\\\.claude\\skills\\reflect\\scripts\\hook-stop.bat",
        "timeout": 5000
      }]
    }]
  }
}
```

**Current state:** Manual `/reflect` works, but automatic reflection at session end won't trigger until the hook is configured.

